          <outline text="供燃气用地（U13）：分输站、门站、储气站、加气母站、液化石油气储配站、灌瓶站和地面输气管廊等设施用地，不包括制气厂用地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BE%9B%E7%87%83%E6%B0%94%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%88U13%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A%E5%88%86%E8%BE%93%E7%AB%99%E3%80%81%E9%97%A8%E7%AB%99%E3%80%81%E5%82%A8%E6%B0%94%E7%AB%99%E3%80%81%E5%8A%A0%E6%B0%94%E6%AF%8D%E7%AB%99%E3%80%81%E6%B6%B2%E5%8C%96%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9%E6%B0%94%E5%82%A8%E9%85%8D%E7%AB%99%E3%80%81%E7%81%8C%E7%93%B6%E7%AB%99%E5%92%8C%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E8%BE%93%E6%B0%94%E7%AE%A1%E5%BB%8A%E7%AD%89%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%88%B6%E6%B0%94%E5%8E%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="供热用地（U14）：集中供热锅炉房、热力站、换热站和地面输热管廊等设施用地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BE%9B%E7%83%AD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%88U14%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E4%BE%9B%E7%83%AD%E9%94%85%E7%82%89%E6%88%BF%E3%80%81%E7%83%AD%E5%8A%9B%E7%AB%99%E3%80%81%E6%8D%A2%E7%83%AD%E7%AB%99%E5%92%8C%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E8%BE%93%E7%83%AD%E7%AE%A1%E5%BB%8A%E7%AD%89%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="通信用地（U15）：邮政中心局、部政支局、部件处理中心、电信局、移动基站、微波站等设施用地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%A1%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%88U15%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A%E9%82%AE%E6%94%BF%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E5%B1%80%E3%80%81%E9%83%A8%E6%94%BF%E6%94%AF%E5%B1%80%E3%80%81%E9%83%A8%E4%BB%B6%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E3%80%81%E7%94%B5%E4%BF%A1%E5%B1%80%E3%80%81%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E5%9F%BA%E7%AB%99%E3%80%81%E5%BE%AE%E6%B3%A2%E7%AB%99%E7%AD%89%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="广播电视用地（U16）：广播电视的发射、传输和监测设施用地，包括无线电收信区、发信区以及广播电视发射台、转播台、差转台、监测站等设施用地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B9%BF%E6%92%AD%E7%94%B5%E8%A7%86%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%88U16%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A%E5%B9%BF%E6%92%AD%E7%94%B5%E8%A7%86%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B0%84%E3%80%81%E4%BC%A0%E8%BE%93%E5%92%8C%E7%9B%91%E6%B5%8B%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E6%97%A0%E7%BA%BF%E7%94%B5%E6%94%B6%E4%BF%A1%E5%8C%BA%E3%80%81%E5%8F%91%E4%BF%A1%E5%8C%BA%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E5%B9%BF%E6%92%AD%E7%94%B5%E8%A7%86%E5%8F%91%E5%B0%84%E5%8F%B0%E3%80%81%E8%BD%AC%E6%92%AD%E5%8F%B0%E3%80%81%E5%B7%AE%E8%BD%AC%E5%8F%B0%E3%80%81%E7%9B%91%E6%B5%8B%E7%AB%99%E7%AD%89%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        </outline>
        <outline text="环境设施用地（U2）：雨水、污水、固体废物处理等环境保护设施及其附属设施用地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%88U2%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A%E9%9B%A8%E6%B0%B4%E3%80%81%E6%B1%A1%E6%B0%B4%E3%80%81%E5%9B%BA%E4%BD%93%E5%BA%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E7%AD%89%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E9%99%84%E5%B1%9E%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
          <outline text="排水用地（U21）：雨水泵站、湾水泵站、湾水处理、湾泥处理厂等设施及其附属的构筑物用地，不包括排水河渠用地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%B4%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%88U21%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A%E9%9B%A8%E6%B0%B4%E6%B3%B5%E7%AB%99%E3%80%81%E6%B9%BE%E6%B0%B4%E6%B3%B5%E7%AB%99%E3%80%81%E6%B9%BE%E6%B0%B4%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E3%80%81%E6%B9%BE%E6%B3%A5%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%8E%82%E7%AD%89%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E9%99%84%E5%B1%9E%E7%9A%84%E6%9E%84%E7%AD%91%E7%89%A9%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%B4%E6%B2%B3%E6%B8%A0%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="环卫用地（U23）：生活垃圾、医疗垃圾、危险废物处理（置），以及垃圾转适、公属、车辆清洗、环卫车辆停放修理等设施用地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%8E%AF%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%88U23%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E3%80%81%E5%8C%BB%E7%96%97%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E3%80%81%E5%8D%B1%E9%99%A9%E5%BA%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%EF%BC%88%E7%BD%AE%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E8%BD%AC%E9%80%82%E3%80%81%E5%85%AC%E5%B1%9E%E3%80%81%E8%BD%A6%E8%BE%86%E6%B8%85%E6%B4%97%E3%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%8D%AB%E8%BD%A6%E8%BE%86%E5%81%9C%E6%94%BE%E4%BF%AE%E7%90%86%E7%AD%89%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        </outline>
        <outline text="安全设施用地（U3）：消防、防洪等保卫城市安全的公用设施及其附属设施用地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%88U3%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E3%80%81%E9%98%B2%E6%B4%AA%E7%AD%89%E4%BF%9D%E5%8D%AB%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AC%E7%94%A8%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E9%99%84%E5%B1%9E%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
          <outline text="消防用地（U31）：消防站、消防通信及指辉训练中心等设施用地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%88U31%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E7%AB%99%E3%80%81%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%A1%E5%8F%8A%E6%8C%87%E8%BE%89%E8%AE%AD%E7%BB%83%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E7%AD%89%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="防洪用地（U32）：防滨提、防洪枢妞、排洪沟渠等设施用地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%98%B2%E6%B4%AA%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%88U32%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A%E9%98%B2%E6%BB%A8%E6%8F%90%E3%80%81%E9%98%B2%E6%B4%AA%E6%9E%A2%E5%A6%9E%E3%80%81%E6%8E%92%E6%B4%AA%E6%B2%9F%E6%B8%A0%E7%AD%89%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        </outline>
        <outline text="其他公用设施用地（U9）：除以上之外的公用设施用地，包括施工、养护、维修等设施用地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%85%AC%E7%94%A8%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%88U9%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A%E9%99%A4%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E4%B9%8B%E5%A4%96%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AC%E7%94%A8%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E3%80%81%E5%85%BB%E6%8A%A4%E3%80%81%E7%BB%B4%E4%BF%AE%E7%AD%89%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="绿地与广场用地（G）：公园绿地、防护绿地、广场等公共开放空间用地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8E%E5%B9%BF%E5%9C%BA%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%88G%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%AC%E5%9B%AD%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E9%98%B2%E6%8A%A4%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E5%B9%BF%E5%9C%BA%E7%AD%89%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
          <outline text="公因绿地（G1）：向公众开放，以游胞为主要功能，兼具生态、美化、防灾等作用的绿地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%AC%E5%9B%A0%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%88G1%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A%E5%90%91%E5%85%AC%E4%BC%97%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E6%B8%B8%E8%83%9E%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%BC%E5%85%B7%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E3%80%81%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96%E3%80%81%E9%98%B2%E7%81%BE%E7%AD%89%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="防护绿地（G2）：具有卫生、隔离和安全防护功能的绿地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%98%B2%E6%8A%A4%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%88G2%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E3%80%81%E9%9A%94%E7%A6%BB%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%98%B2%E6%8A%A4%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="广场用地（G3）：以游憩、纪念、集会和避借子功能为主的城市公共活动场地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B9%BF%E5%9C%BA%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%88G3%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A%E4%BB%A5%E6%B8%B8%E6%86%A9%E3%80%81%E7%BA%AA%E5%BF%B5%E3%80%81%E9%9B%86%E4%BC%9A%E5%92%8C%E9%81%BF%E5%80%9F%E5%AD%90%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E5%9C%BA%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        </outline>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="注：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B3%A8%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="1.《中华人民共和国土地管理法》中将用地分为三大类：农用地、建设用地和未利用地；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E3%80%8A%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%8E%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E5%9B%BD%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E6%B3%95%E3%80%8B%E4%B8%AD%E5%B0%86%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E7%B1%BB%EF%BC%9A%E5%86%9C%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%92%8C%E6%9C%AA%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="2.“特殊用地”（H4）中“安保用地”（H42）不包括公安局，该用地应归入“行政办公用地”（A1）；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E2%80%9C%E7%89%B9%E6%AE%8A%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%88H4%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%AD%E2%80%9C%E5%AE%89%E4%BF%9D%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%88H42%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%8D%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%8C%E8%AF%A5%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%92%E5%85%A5%E2%80%9C%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E5%8A%9E%E5%85%AC%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%88A1%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="3.已用作其他用途的文物古迹用地应按其实际用途归类；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E5%B7%B2%E7%94%A8%E4%BD%9C%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E7%94%A8%E9%80%94%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E7%89%A9%E5%8F%A4%E8%BF%B9%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%BA%94%E6%8C%89%E5%85%B6%E5%AE%9E%E9%99%85%E7%94%A8%E9%80%94%E5%BD%92%E7%B1%BB%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="如北京的故宫和颐和园均是国家级重点文物古迹，但故宫用作博物院，而颐和园用作公园，因此应分别归为“图书展览用地”和“公园绿地”，而不是归为“文物古迹用地”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A6%82%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E7%9A%84%E6%95%85%E5%AE%AB%E5%92%8C%E9%A2%90%E5%92%8C%E5%9B%AD%E5%9D%87%E6%98%AF%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E7%BA%A7%E9%87%8D%E7%82%B9%E6%96%87%E7%89%A9%E5%8F%A4%E8%BF%B9%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E6%95%85%E5%AE%AB%E7%94%A8%E4%BD%9C%E5%8D%9A%E7%89%A9%E9%99%A2%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E9%A2%90%E5%92%8C%E5%9B%AD%E7%94%A8%E4%BD%9C%E5%85%AC%E5%9B%AD%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%A0%E6%AD%A4%E5%BA%94%E5%88%86%E5%88%AB%E5%BD%92%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9C%E5%9B%BE%E4%B9%A6%E5%B1%95%E8%A7%88%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E2%80%9D%E5%92%8C%E2%80%9C%E5%85%AC%E5%9B%AD%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E5%BD%92%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9C%E6%96%87%E7%89%A9%E5%8F%A4%E8%BF%B9%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="4规划建设用地标准" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="4.1一般规定" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4.1%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="4.1.1用地面积应按平面投影计算。每块用地只可计算一次，不得重复。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4.1.1%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E5%BA%94%E6%8C%89%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E6%8A%95%E5%BD%B1%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E3%80%82%E6%AF%8F%E5%9D%97%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8F%AA%E5%8F%AF%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%8D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="4.1.2城市（镇）总体规划宜采用1/10000或1/5000比例尺的图纸进行建设用地分类计算，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4.1.2%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%88%E9%95%87%EF%BC%89%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%AE%9C%E9%87%87%E7%94%A81/10000%E6%88%961/5000%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E5%B0%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="控制性详细规划宜采用1/2000或1/1000比例尺的图纸进行用地分类计算。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E6%80%A7%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%AE%9C%E9%87%87%E7%94%A81/2000%E6%88%961/1000%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E5%B0%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="现状和规划的用地分类计算应采用同一比例尺。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%8E%B0%E7%8A%B6%E5%92%8C%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E5%BA%94%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%80%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E5%B0%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="4.1.3用地的计量单位应为万平方米（公顷），代码为“hm2”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4.1.3%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%A1%E9%87%8F%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E5%BA%94%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%87%E5%B9%B3%E6%96%B9%E7%B1%B3%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E9%A1%B7%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9Chm2%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="数字统计精度应根据图纸比例尺确定，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1%E7%B2%BE%E5%BA%A6%E5%BA%94%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E5%B0%BA%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="1/10000图纸应精确至个位，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1/10000%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%E5%BA%94%E7%B2%BE%E7%A1%AE%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%AA%E4%BD%8D%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
